Title: Relates to the substitution of brand name epinephrine auto-injectors with alternate epinephrine auto-injectors
Summary: Relates to the substitution of brand name epinephrine auto-injectors with alternate epinephrine auto-injectors in certain cases.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the substitution of brand name epinephrine auto-injectors with alternate epinephrine auto-injectors for dispensation by pharmacists
